thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Paul Nelson

author: Paul Nelson
title: Paul Nelson
text:
ORDERED TWO WEEKS AGO - Still awaiting the delivery of the INK to Home ..POOR, POOR SERVICE ...Likely not to use you again
Further to my concerns on delivery yes it was delivered yesterday BUT there have been numerous false starts to deliver..suggest you speak to the couriers you employ on , as it sounds thru their questionable communicating systems (interstate offices of courier - pick up calls on delivery-no idea where the suburbs are to deliver in different states) that the loading of my purchased ink has been to many & varied parts of this great state / country we live in .... (as it so happens had to purchase ink to sustain the printer / printing from Office works !)...
